## After completing plan — save to memory

Save a structured summary to `memory/weekly-plans/YYYY-Wxx.md` (for weekly) or `memory/weekly-plans/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (for daily) with this format:

```markdown
# [Weekly Plan — YYYY-Wxx] or [Daily Plan — YYYY-MM-DD]

**Date:** YYYY-MM-DD

## Previous Plan Status
- [Item]: ✅ Done | 🔄 Carried over | ⚠️ Blocked | ❌ Dropped

## This Period's Plan
### P0 — Strategic Focus
1. [Action] — [goal alignment]

### P1 — Important
- [Action]

### Backlog
- [Action]

## Goal Progress
- [Goal 1]: [status emoji] [note]

## Context Inputs
- **Feedback signals used:** [yes/no — key themes if yes]
- **Decisions referenced:** [list any from memory/decisions/]
- **Carried from last period:** [items]
```

This file will be read by future planning runs, the exec update generator, and the retrospective agent.

